snippet.title: Constructions Perpendicular Bisector (Geometry)
snippet.description:
Learn how to Construct a Perpendicular Bisector using a compass and straightedge in this free math video tutorial by Mario's Math Tutoring.

0:01 How to Construct a Perpendicular Bisector with Compass & Straight Edge
0:28 Make an Arc From Each Endpoint of the Segment
1:21 Draw the Perpendicular Bisector Where the 2 Arcs Intersect
